Items.Title: Resolution calling on the New York State Legislature to pass and the Governor to sign A.9861/S.7015, legislation which would amend the State Education Law enabling New York City to require that all 5 year old children in the City attend kindergarten.
Items.ActionText: This Resolution was Hearing Held by Committee
Items.MatterName: Enabling NYC to require that all 5 year old children in the City attend kindergarten. (A.9861/S.7015)
